column5: hey whose gonna be at the islands tommoro morning? ill be getting out there for first time in a long time, hopefully ill get into some pike for once, whos coming out?
Where do you go to board the ferry and at what time does it leave?

hey clampet, ferry docks are at the foot of bay st. The first one tommorow is at 6 35, ill be taking the 8 am for wards island. heres the schedule  Ferry Schedule  Looks like i ont be seeing anyone out there  lol More fish for me  aha

Have fun at the islands.  Won't be out there now until next year.  Just got back from fishing in Barrie and need a few days to thaw out - us Brits are not used to fishing all day in -12 wind chill! :-)
If I didnt live so far i'd join you for sure, maybe some other time..
oops I'm too late for this thread.  dsn
ahah    DSN, ill be going out at least 1 more time this week... maye we can arrange something?
